            <td style="BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: ; BORDER-TOP-COLOR: ; BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: ; BORDER-LEFT-COLOR:"
                valign="top"
                align="left">
                <p align="justify">Nowadays, hand held metal detectors have become an important item from the point
                of view of security operations and procedures.</p>

                <p align="justify">A hand held metal detector can be used in government institutions or in schools
                and in most of the institutions.</p>

                <p align="justify">The society we live in demands that we try to protect the ones around us all the
                time and it also demands that we take the necessary measures to protect ourselves.</p>

                <p align="justify">These <a style="COLOR: #064b8c; TEXT-DECORATION: underline"
                   href="professional_metal_detector.html">professional metal detectors</a> items help with
                   identifying and locating different objects, therefore stopping their owners from using them.</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </tbody>
</table>

<p align="justify">Many institutions make use of a hand held metal detector in order to ensure the security of
those working or entering those particular institutions. Such examples would be hospitals, courtrooms, jails,
warehouses, airports, embassies, schools, different venues organizing different events, any type of correctional
institutions and so on. These locations consider hand held metal detectors one of their main means of ensuring
their people&rsquo;s security.</p>

<p align="justify"><img style="WIDTH: 300px; HEIGHT: 198px"
     title="Image of Hand Held Metal Detector."
     border="0"
     hspace="10"
     alt="Image of Hand Held Metal Detector."
     align="left"
     src="images/hand_held_metal_detector.jpg"></p>

<p align="justify">A hand held metal detector can also have another function than that of ensuring protection. Some
use these items for relaxing in their spare time, locating different items using these detectors in parks, on the
beach or even at home. Our website provides various useful pieces of information hand held metal detectors and
their functions.</p>

<p align="justify">It is well-known that technology is never in standby and so is the case of the industry of hand
held metal detectors. This industry perfects this kind of items every day, improving their level of efficiency and
ensuring more and more protection of all locations all the time. Unfortunately, this aspect is absolutely necessary
in the society we live in at the moment, an incredible number of situations being able to put us in danger in any
moment.</p>

<p align="justify">The use of a <a style="COLOR: #094a8c; TEXT-DECORATION: underline"
   href="http://www.henrys.co.uk/cctv/handheldbodyscanner.htm"
   target="_new">hand held metal detector</a> has increased due to the numerous events which have occurred
   throughout our entire history, events which have brought some light as far as the necessity of being safe and
   secure is concerned. Hand held metal detector are most frequently used in airports, with the purpose of
   preventing any unpleasant situations which can have incredibly unfortunate consequences, such as terrorist
   attacks or attacks of any other kind. This industry has known an outstanding growth since the incidents from
   World Trade Centre, one of the most frightful and marking incidents in history. Hand held metal detectors have
   succeeded in preventing multiple unpleasant situations since that particular one.</p>

<p align="justify">These security items have become more and more useful and more and more necessary, there being
different kinds of metal detectors to be used for ensuring the necessary protection and safety. A hand held metal
detector is also useful when it comes to kids or youngsters having access to guns and other such dangerous weapons
and getting crazy ideas of bringing them into all kinds of public institutions, from government buildings to
schools or hospitals.</p>  
